{"tid":32250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：有騙子形容警隊是黑警　小撮人散播謠言","createTime":"2016-12-10T05:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T09:04:29.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71c970c8f847d88da21d2c5cab3dabe2d59285a3","tid":32250,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:44:05.000Z","msg":"政務司司長林鄭月娥在滅罪委員會聯席會議時表示，社會上有小撮人散播謠言指警隊濫權，近年示威活動倍增，令警隊面對很大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，有騙子形容警隊是黑警，香港警隊面臨挑戰，每次遊行都有風險，她認為警隊是遊行人士的好朋友，在示威前做大量工作，壓力好大。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又說，警隊近年在人手編制上出現政治干預，增設職位時受到立法會阻延，但她仍然預計下年度警隊人手資源會再上升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1301488-20161210.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1301488-20161210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=irRdMQeoJttM%2B9kmMWQUZEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=8ae54daa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1301488-20161210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=993642d5\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1301488-20161210.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4079e2a87ae7d242e95f9e32adcdf35953f9b588","tid":32250,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5becf57eb781ab99f867efaa16f927809b598bbb","tid":32250,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c30678b9273f2b4e219e78087a976917b0f317c","tid":32250,"uid":56998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:56:04.000Z","msg":"一定係&quot;休班警&quot;犯罪集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25a68fe1a6ce6f9a6d9bcfd179e5fd28be4c839","tid":32250,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10